document_data.name: Tsui Tong
document_data.mainbody:
The '''Tsui Tong''' was the primary criminal organization of the province of [[Kao Shan]] in the [[Shou Lung]] empire.

It was based out of the city of [[Kai Shan]] and had become a political force in the area<ref>
